Bayerische Volkspartei Abstract: Poster shows a man in red running from a deluge of blue and white pieces of paper marked Bayerische Volkspartei. Text: The election storm is sweeping the land! Bavarian blue and white against Russian red! Bavarian People's Party. Physical description: 1 print (poster) : lithograph, color ; 100 x 74 cm.
